11
00:00:29.203 --> 00:00:31.901
-[Martian] Who's this?
-[Naomi] Hassan Zamani.

12
00:00:32.162 --> 00:00:34.338
Youngest son of a powerful
political clan.

13
00:00:35.426 --> 00:00:37.254
Hassan just attacked Buzzard.

14
00:00:37.515 --> 00:00:40.736
