Go ahead. laugh it up.

35
00:01:47.281 --> 00:01:48.717
I'm sorry.

36
00:01:48.890 --> 00:01:50.458
No. please.

37
00:01:50.719 --> 00:01:52.155
[laughs]

38
00:01:52.329 --> 00:01:53.634
I'm so sorry.

39
00:01:53.939 --> 00:01:55.811
Who doesn't enjoy
the misfortune of others?

40
00:01:55.985 --> 00:01:58.596
Also. I'm never
normally this funny.

41
00:01:59.815 --> 00:02:02.644
Where I'm from.
now you make a wish.

42
00:02:03.471 --> 00:02:06.038
I wish the last
30 seconds never happened.

43
00:02:07.083 --> 00:02:09.128
You sure about that?

44
00:02:11.131 --> 00:02:12.523
Anyway. you blew it.

45
00:02:12.741 --> 00:02:15.744
You have to close your eyes
and say it here.

46
00:02:15.918 --> 00:02:17.920
Otherwise. it won't come true.

47
00:02:19.313 --> 00:02:21.532
[laughs softly]

48
00:02:24.927 --> 00:02:26.537
Too late.

49
00:02:26.711 --> 00:02:27.711
You missed it.

50
00:02:27.799 --> 00:02:28.974
[chuckles]

51
00:02:29.149 --> 00:02:30.498
What. I don't
get a second chance?

52
00:02:30.672 --> 00:02:32.587
It doesn't work like that.

53
00:02:33.675 --> 00:02:35.546
If I beg?

54
00:02:36.852 --> 00:02:40.029
You can't bargain with fate.

55
00:02:40.203 --> 00:02:41.563
You're just
going to have to accept

56
00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:43.119
that what
just happened happened.

57
00:02:43.293 --> 00:02:45.339
and there's nothing
you can do about it.

58
